<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/mycokeys.100.106709.plate3>
    dc:description "Plate 3. Hydnotrya laojunshanensis A young sarcomata cut in half B mature ascomata with one cut in half C infolded and chambered ascoma D section of hymenium in 5 % KOH E a peridium section in 5 % KOH F ascospores released from asci in 5 % KOH G-I ascospores under SEM (I. SEM of a single ascospore cut in half). Scale bars: 1 cm (A, B); 50 μm (D, E); 20 μm (F); 5 μm (G-I)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/935611" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

